{"tid":1687200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「佔旺畫家」涉警總外襲警等9罪　還押至明年2月27日開審","createTime":"2019-11-01T16:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T17:18:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3c8840cc6cb14be5c0ca9a2bf4226ccee5d30755","tid":1687200,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:05:44.000Z","msg":"於一連串反對修訂《逃犯條例》示威衝突中首名被檢控的「佔旺畫家」潘浩超，因涉6月21日在警察總部外襲擊7名警務人員、毀壞警總外牆和扶手電梯、以粗言辱罵警務人員和向他們展示不文手勢等，被控1項參與未經批准集結、1項刑事毀壞罪及7項襲警罪<br />\n<br />\n控方表示將傳召15名警察證人，並有長約2小時的事發片段，預計審期7至8天。辯方表示不爭議被告身份及涉案片段真確性，案件現押後明年2月27日轉到西九龍法院開審，期間被告繼續還押監房看管。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3d742e8592c8ef4ea37ef62c3245f032c8b51f","tid":1687200,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2bb6600181ae6bc82b714674828ad5521e9eaf3","tid":1687200,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"畫家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb568b6cc4e3a43769cef6b7289e0ec9d526ad0","tid":1687200,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecb0ae39f259fa8097de5192de3506e843e20fb7","tid":1687200,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b3d742e8592c8ef4ea37ef62c3245f032c8b51f","tid":1687200,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-